attribute.description_en:
The HISS subsystem is subjected to real fault injection attacks (usually due to hardware issues):
 a. The SUBCTRL register in the HISS subsystem experiences a parity error due to fault injection;
 b. The HISS subsystem is subjected to real fault injection attacks, causing abnormal efuse operations;
 c. The internal bus of the HISS subsystem is subjected to real fault injection attacks;
 d. The internal SRAM of the HISS subsystem is subjected to real fault injection attacks.
